Class Title

java.lang.Object
  greenfoot.Actor
      Title

public class Title
extends greenfoot.Actor

The game logo for the title screen. This object animates in by moving -150 along the y-axis, and by fading in over 120 frames. After 60 frames, it will spawn a TitleFlare object.
